## üß† Overview

This project demonstrates how to build a complete CRUD system using **FastAPI** as the backend framework and **Svelte** as the frontend framework.

The backend handles authentication (JWT), user management, and database communication, while the frontend provides an elegant and interactive UI for consuming the API.

